  <brief_title>Prognostic Impact of Anatomical Resection Vs. Non-anatomical Resection for HCC</brief_title>
  <acronym>ARversusNAR</acronym>
  <official_title>Anatomical Liver Resection by Means of Ultrasound-guided Vessel Compression Versus Non-anatomical Resection for Hepatocellular Carcinoma: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
