  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patient affected by single HCC

          -  patients in whom liver resection is indicated

          -  HCC without vascular invasion and/or thrombosis

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  multinodular HCC

          -  metastatic disease

          -  spontaneous tumor rupture
      </textblock>
